data.description: Come live in the most unique boutique condominium nestled in between Buckhead and Brookhaven. Location cannot be beat! Walk to a plethora of restaurants and shopping (Phipps Plaza)  within blocks away from the condo. The interior consists of high end renovations - luxury lvp flooring, recessed lighting, 4-inch granite countertops in kitchen. The wood burning fireplace for your chilly days with built in bookcases around.  10 ft ceilings throughout with double French doors to Juliet balcony and unique light fixtures throughout. The master bathroom has been transformed into a spa like retreat with carrera marble tiles in zero entry shower from floor to ceiling. Access to the rooftop of the building is right from the owners room. For your wardrobe - there's a walk in closet , built in wardrobe in bedroom and 2 additional closets in bathrooms. Kitchen layout is functional and all appliances have only been less than a year old ! Building has new elevators, new exterior paint, new windows and French doors just installed last spring! Assessments has been all paid for the new projects. New owner just has to move in. Hurry and come see this unique beauty in person for yourself !
